snippet.title: Taito Variety Pack multi-menu (タイトーバラエティーパック) (Game Boy)
snippet.description:
An official Game Boy multi-cart of Bubble Bobble, Elevator Action, Taito Chase H.Q. (Chase H.Q.) and Sagaia (Darius II).

The Taito Variety Pack uses the unique MMM01 Game Boy mapper (similar to M161) also used by Momotaro Collection 2, believed to be responsible for the multi-menu (the multi-menu also seems to be similar to the Mani 4-in-1 menu). Hence, emulators might fail to load it or just skip to one of the games contained.
